OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 20 APR
OL,4,CTEST CARDS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1964FBBC Test Card E is introduced.
OL,7,
OL,8,FThe design was intended for use on the
OL,9,F625-line UHF system, used by BBC Two.
OL,10,
OL,11,FReports regarding the length of service
OL,12,Fof this design vary - some claim it was
OL,13,Fwithdrawn after only one day, others
OL,14,Fsay it remained in use for about a
OL,15,Fmonth.
OL,16,
OL,17,FIts replacement was a modified version
OL,18,Fof Test Card C, which remained in use
OL,19,Funtil 1967, when Test Card F came
OL,20,Falong.
OL,21,
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
